## Violation handling

Phase 3.5 Quality Gate Pass 4 detect banned phrases:

```yaml
pass_4_banned_prose:
  violations:
    - section: "tkcs.technology_rationale"
      phrase: "hiện đại"
      occurrences: 3
      severity: major
      fix: |
        Thay "Công nghệ hiện đại, mạnh mẽ, đồng bộ..."
        Bằng: "Next.js 15 (SSR + Server Components), NestJS 10.3 (DI + modular),
        PostgreSQL 16 (JSONB + logical replication) — stack released ≤12 tháng."
```

Score penalty: -10 per banned phrase occurrence (capped at -30).

Score < 80 → User prompt: "Prose quality below threshold. Re-generate with stricter prompt? (y/n)"
